    evaluation: `The candidate should propose a methodology for valuing an intangible asset like a brand logo. Potential approaches include: royalty relief method (estimating the royalties NBC would save by owning the logo vs. licensing it), income approach (estimating the incremental revenue or profit generated by products bearing the logo), market approach (looking at comparable brand valuations, though direct comparisons might be difficult for a logo itself), or cost approach (cost to recreate the brand, less relevant here). The candidate should discuss the factors that contribute to brand value (recognition, reputation, emotional connection) and how these might translate into financial terms.`,
